headline: Airbnb Experiences Relaunch: This Is What It’s Likely Going to Look Like
summary: Airbnb will try to widen its experiences audience by crafting them for locals, as well as travelers. Experiences will get the "categories" treatment, and a dose of TikTok and Instagram stories-like marketing.
